<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=2385&amp;p=13989#p13989"><![CDATA[
To use .skin files, you must extract (or copy-paste) them to C:\Program Files\Classic Shell\Skins. .skin files are for the Classic styles of the menu (Classic single or two columns). You can't use them with the Windows 7 style of the menu. Windows 7 style uses the .skin7 format.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=54">Gaurav</a> — Wed Jul 16, 2014 1:53 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
